Here's a list of 50 "message of the day" quotes inspired by characters from "The Sopranos," formatted as an array of JSON objects:

```json
[
    {"message": "You want the truth? You can’t handle the truth!", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "In this world, you either take or you get taken.", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "Whatever you do, don’t be a rat.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "Sometimes it’s good to be a little selfish.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "Family is everything, even when it’s a pain.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "You gotta always be working the angles.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "Don’t let anybody tell you how to run your life.", "author": "Hesh Rabkin"},
    {"message": "A man’s gotta do what a man’s gotta do.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "Life’s too short for regrets.", "author": "Dr. Melfi"},
    {"message": "Sometimes you have to take a step back to go forward.", "author": "Anthony Jr."},
    {"message": "You never know how strong you are until being strong is your only choice.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "Fear makes you weak.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "The reward is in the risk.", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "Every day’s a new opportunity.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "You can’t enjoy the sweet without the sour.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "Sometimes you gotta do something bad for a good reason.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "A loyalty to the family comes first.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "Stick to your principles, no matter the cost.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "You can’t turn your back on your family.", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "It’s all about the hustle.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "Success is a journey, not a destination.", "author": "Hesh Rabkin"},
    {"message": "Life’s a game, play it wisely.", "author": "Dr. Melfi"},
    {"message": "Don’t take sh*t from anyone.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "Keep your enemies close; keep your friends closer.", "author": "Michael Corleone"},
    {"message": "Every choice has its consequences.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "Improvise, adapt, overcome.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "Trust is fragile; don’t break it.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "Change is the only constant.", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "Sometimes you gotta roll the dice.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "You can’t be afraid of the darkness.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "Never forget where you came from.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "Keep your eyes on the prize.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "You’re never too old to learn something new.", "author": "Hesh Rabkin"},
    {"message": "Every dog has its day.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "Loyalty is everything in our world.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "You still think of me as a kid?", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "You always have a choice.", "author": "Dr. Melfi"},
    {"message": "There’s no easy way out.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "Don’t confuse between being kind and being weak.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "Learn to roll with the punches.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "Don’t let anyone dictate your path.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
    {"message": "A wise man knows he knows nothing.", "author": "Hesh Rabkin"},
    {"message": "You gotta be tough to survive.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "You can’t change the past, but you can shape your future.", "author": "Dr. Melfi"},
    {"message": "Life is full of surprises; embrace them.", "author": "Christopher Moltisanti"},
    {"message": "Know your worth and don’t settle.", "author": "Carmela Soprano"},
    {"message": "You’ll never get anywhere playing it safe.", "author": "Silvio Dante"},
    {"message": "Face your fears head-on.", "author": "Tony Soprano"},
    {"message": "What doesn’t kill you makes you stronger.", "author": "Paulie 'Walnuts' Gualtieri"},
```
